            Edward Hillenaar
          
          
            
              I am a classically trained data scientist living in the
              Netherlands in a town called Zwaag. Currently I work in my
              own practice as a psychologist/therapist and I’m writing a
              doctoral thesis on the nature and origin of
              consciousness.
